<seg id="509">Question 734 – 4(3): Rankin Inlet’s Hamlet Office (Sammurtok, A)</seg>
<seg id="510">My question is to the Minister of Community and Government Services.</seg>
<seg id="511">As the minister is aware, Rankin Inlet’s hamlet office was recently assessed to determine the extent of the facility’s deterioration.</seg>
