<seg id="515">I can inform the member that yes, we have been talking with the hamlet with the mould problems in the municipal office there and a company did check it out and there is mould.</seg>
<seg id="516">What we’re going to do is work with the hamlet to try to remediate the mould come summer. That’s the most update I have right now to help them out with mould remediation.</seg>
